---

<Layout
  title="Living in Zurich Guide 2024 | Essential Tips for Expats"
  description="Complete guide to living in Zurich for expats. Expert advice on housing, healthcare, neighborhoods, and more. Updated for 2024 with current insights and tips."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dphbnwjtx/image/upload/v1740598472/henrique-ferreira-6v-K4PpCHVw-unsplash_1_zkpj2a.webp"
        alt="Zurich cityscape with lake"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/60 to-black/40"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
          <span class="block">Living in Zurich</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">Complete Guide for <span class="text-primary-500">Expats</span></span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-xl text-gray-300">
          Your comprehensive guide to life in Switzerland's largest city. From housing to healthcare, discover everything you need to know about Zurich.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Quick Stats -->
        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {quickStats.map(stat => (
            <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4">
              <dt class="text-gray-300 text-sm">{stat.label}</dt>
              <dd class="text-white font-bold text-xl">{stat.value}</dd>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Introduction to Zurich</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg">
          <p>
            Zurich, Switzerland's largest city and financial capital, consistently ranks among the world's most livable cities. With its stunning location on Lake Zurich, surrounded by the Alps, the city offers an exceptional quality of life, combining urban sophistication with natural beauty.
          </p>
          <p>
            Home to numerous multinational companies, leading universities, and a thriving startup scene, Zurich attracts professionals from around the globe. The city's efficient public transport, excellent healthcare system, and high standard of living make it particularly attractive to expats.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Living in Zurich -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Living in Zurich</h2>
        
        <!-- PrimeRelocation.ch Highlight Box -->
        <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 border-2 border-primary-200">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900">Expert Tip: Use PrimeRelocation.ch</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-primary-700">
                For hassle-free housing search in Zurich, we recommend <a href="https://www.primerelocation.ch" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">PrimeRelocation.ch</a>. Their specialized service for expats includes:
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li class="flex items-center text-primary-700">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Premium property listings
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-primary-700">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  English-speaking support
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-primary-700">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Full relocation assistance
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Neighborhood Guide -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Neighborhoods Overview</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
          {neighborhoodGuide.map(neighborhood => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">{neighborhood.name}</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">{neighborhood.description}</p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
